reviewText: Great movie the otherside of Joan
Very happy , arrived in record time, love it,

This is a great film; one of those type where even as Joan's character her husband is attempting to murder her still the movie stays consistently light and crazy; the supporting cast is great and of course Joan is gold; I miss her so much!!
Great deal on two hard to find movies. Very, very satisfied with my purchase. Fast shipping!!!!!!
So glad I purchased these. Great addition to my collection of Joan Rivers. I would say they are a must for any Joan Rivers fan.

Great value, high quality, packaged separately in sturdy cases. I played both dvds on a Blu Ray DVD player and was pleased with both video and audio quality. Will make a fine addition to your Joan Rivers collection.
